# Skill Enforcement Rule

Before writing ANY code, making ANY design decision, or proposing ANY fix,
you MUST read every skill file listed below using the ReadFile tool.
Do not summarize, skip, or assume their contents from their names.
Treat each skill file as a mandatory briefing document.

